{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":965,"text":"I could never have imagined"},{"time":3531,"text":"that a 19-year-old suicide bomber"},{"time":7507,"text":"would actually teach me a valuable lesson."},{"time":12640,"text":"But he did."},{"time":14640,"text":"He taught me to never presume anything"},{"time":19283,"text":"about anyone you don't know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24414,"text":"On a Thursday morning in July 2005,"},{"time":28567,"text":"the bomber and I, unknowingly,"},{"time":31649,"text":"boarded the same train carriage\nat the same time,"},{"time":36220,"text":"standing, apparently, just feet apart."},{"time":42345,"text":"I didn't see him."},{"time":44185,"text":"Actually, I didn't see anyone."},{"time":46000,"text":"You know not to look\nat anyone on the Tube,"},{"time":48611,"text":"but I guess he saw me."},{"time":52916,"text":"I guess he looked at all of us,"},{"time":56687,"text":"as his hand hovered\nover the detonation switch."},{"time":62439,"text":"I've often wondered: What was he thinking?"},{"time":66908,"text":"Especially in those final seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72765,"text":"I know it wasn't personal."},{"time":74977,"text":"He didn't set out to kill\nor maim me, Gill Hicks."},{"time":79018,"text":"I mean -- he didn't know me."},{"time":81758,"text":"No."},{"time":83666,"text":"Instead, he gave me"},{"time":86636,"text":"an unwarranted and an unwanted label."},{"time":92272,"text":"I had become the enemy."},{"time":97390,"text":"To him, I was the \"other,\""},{"time":100990,"text":"the \"them,\" as opposed to \"us.\""},{"time":105581,"text":"The label \"enemy\" allowed him\nto dehumanize us."},{"time":111674,"text":"It allowed him to push that button."},{"time":115339,"text":"And he wasn't selective."},{"time":118875,"text":"Twenty-six precious lives were taken\nin my carriage alone,"},{"time":125042,"text":"and I was almost one of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128855,"text":"In the time it takes to draw a breath,"},{"time":131620,"text":"we were plunged into a darkness so immense"},{"time":135314,"text":"that it was almost tangible;"},{"time":137720,"text":"what I imagine wading\nthrough tar might be like."},{"time":143398,"text":"We didn't know we were the enemy."},{"time":146321,"text":"We were just a bunch of commuters\nwho, minutes earlier,"},{"time":150403,"text":"had followed the Tube etiquette:"},{"time":152911,"text":"no direct eye contact,"},{"time":155141,"text":"no talking"},{"time":156894,"text":"and absolutely no conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161948,"text":"But in the lifting of the darkness,"},{"time":165776,"text":"we were reaching out."},{"time":168179,"text":"We were helping each other."},{"time":170808,"text":"We were calling out our names,"},{"time":173293,"text":"a little bit like a roll call,"},{"time":176389,"text":"waiting for responses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180559,"text":"\"I'm Gill. I'm here."},{"time":185111,"text":"I'm alive."},{"time":188279,"text":"OK.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":191697,"text":"\"I'm Gill."},{"time":193679,"text":"Here."},{"time":196318,"text":"Alive."},{"time":199329,"text":"OK.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":203096,"text":"I didn't know Alison."},{"time":206399,"text":"But I listened for her check-ins\nevery few minutes."},{"time":211340,"text":"I didn't know Richard."},{"time":213839,"text":"But it mattered to me that he survived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218752,"text":"All I shared with them"},{"time":220570,"text":"was my first name."},{"time":223013,"text":"They didn't know"},{"time":224188,"text":"that I was a head of a department\nat the Design Council."},{"time":229185,"text":"And here is my beloved briefcase,"},{"time":232766,"text":"also rescued from that morning."},{"time":236479,"text":"They didn't know that I published\narchitecture and design journals,"},{"time":240469,"text":"that I was a Fellow\nof the Royal Society of Arts,"},{"time":243809,"text":"that I wore black --"},{"time":246695,"text":"still do --"},{"time":248566,"text":"that I smoked cigarillos."},{"time":251888,"text":"I don't smoke cigarillos anymore."},{"time":254215,"text":"I drank gin and I watched TED Talks,"},{"time":258423,"text":"of course, never dreaming\nthat one day I would be standing,"},{"time":265593,"text":"balancing on prosthetic legs,"},{"time":268512,"text":"giving a talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270651,"text":"I was a young Australian woman\ndoing extraordinary things in London."},{"time":276319,"text":"And I wasn't ready for that all to end."},{"time":280882,"text":"I was so determined to survive"},{"time":284064,"text":"that I used my scarf to tie tourniquets\naround the tops of my legs,"},{"time":289290,"text":"and I just shut everything\nand everyone out,"},{"time":295345,"text":"to focus, to listen to myself,"},{"time":298629,"text":"to be guided by instinct alone."},{"time":303085,"text":"I lowered my breathing rate."},{"time":305847,"text":"I elevated my thighs."},{"time":307651,"text":"I held myself upright"},{"time":309343,"text":"and I fought the urge to close my eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314681,"text":"I held on for almost an hour,"},{"time":319030,"text":"an hour to contemplate\nthe whole of my life"},{"time":323435,"text":"up until this point."},{"time":327199,"text":"Perhaps I should have done more."},{"time":331223,"text":"Perhaps I could have\nlived more, seen more."},{"time":334451,"text":"Maybe I should have gone running,\ndancing, taken up yoga."},{"time":340317,"text":"But my priority and my focus\nwas always my work."},{"time":345279,"text":"I lived to work."},{"time":347730,"text":"Who I was on my business card"},{"time":350561,"text":"mattered to me."},{"time":353688,"text":"But it didn't matter down in that tunnel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359226,"text":"By the time I felt that first touch"},{"time":363720,"text":"from one of my rescuers,"},{"time":366472,"text":"I was unable to speak,"},{"time":368613,"text":"unable to say even\na small word, like \"Gill.\""},{"time":375183,"text":"I surrendered my body to them."},{"time":377942,"text":"I had done all I possibly could,"},{"time":380839,"text":"and now I was in their hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387091,"text":"I understood"},{"time":389283,"text":"just who and what humanity really is,"},{"time":395972,"text":"when I first saw the ID tag"},{"time":399195,"text":"that was given to me\nwhen I was admitted to hospital."},{"time":402478,"text":"And it read:"},{"time":404218,"text":"\"One unknown estimated female.\""},{"time":411162,"text":"One unknown estimated female."},{"time":417004,"text":"Those four words were my gift."},{"time":421125,"text":"What they told me very clearly"},{"time":423896,"text":"was that my life was saved,"},{"time":426625,"text":"purely because I was a human being."},{"time":430610,"text":"Difference of any kind made no difference"},{"time":434818,"text":"to the extraordinary lengths\nthat the rescuers were prepared to go"},{"time":440129,"text":"to save my life,"},{"time":442458,"text":"to save as many unknowns as they could,"},{"time":445205,"text":"and putting their own lives at risk."},{"time":448405,"text":"To them, it didn't matter\nif I was rich or poor,"},{"time":453298,"text":"the color of my skin,"},{"time":455463,"text":"whether I was male or female,"},{"time":457049,"text":"my sexual orientation,"},{"time":459613,"text":"who I voted for,"},{"time":461240,"text":"whether I was educated,"},{"time":462782,"text":"if I had a faith or no faith at all."},{"time":467409,"text":"Nothing mattered"},{"time":469377,"text":"other than I was a precious human life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475881,"text":"I see myself as a living fact."},{"time":480223,"text":"I am proof"},{"time":482276,"text":"that unconditional love and respect\ncan not only save,"},{"time":489028,"text":"but it can transform lives."},{"time":493226,"text":"Here is a wonderful image\nof one of my rescuers, Andy, and I"},{"time":497718,"text":"taken just last year."},{"time":500080,"text":"Ten years after the event,"},{"time":502665,"text":"and here we are, arm in arm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507559,"text":"Throughout all the chaos,"},{"time":509701,"text":"my hand was held tightly."},{"time":513200,"text":"My face was stroked gently."},{"time":517161,"text":"What did I feel?"},{"time":519541,"text":"I felt loved."},{"time":521685,"text":"What's shielded me from hatred\nand wanting retribution,"},{"time":526526,"text":"what's given me the courage to say:"},{"time":529539,"text":"this ends with me"},{"time":534006,"text":"is love."},{"time":536585,"text":"I was loved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541234,"text":"I believe the potential\nfor widespread positive change"},{"time":547523,"text":"is absolutely enormous"},{"time":549127,"text":"because I know what we're capable of."},{"time":552055,"text":"I know the brilliance of humanity."},{"time":555930,"text":"So this leaves me with some\npretty big things to ponder"},{"time":559864,"text":"and some questions for us all to consider:"},{"time":564512,"text":"Is what unites us not far greater\nthan what can ever divide?"},{"time":571663,"text":"Does it have to take\na tragedy or a disaster"},{"time":575477,"text":"for us to feel deeply\nconnected as one species,"},{"time":580902,"text":"as human beings?"},{"time":583755,"text":"And when will we embrace\nthe wisdom of our era"},{"time":589764,"text":"to rise above mere tolerance"},{"time":593931,"text":"and move to an acceptance"},{"time":596892,"text":"for all who are only a label\nuntil we know them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603550,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604734,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}